column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdAllEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdAllEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.type, p.deVRad_r, p.deVRadErr_r, p.expRad_r, p.expRadErr_r, s.z, s.velDisp, s.velDispErr, g.lgm_tot_p5# p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN photoobj AS p ON p.objID = x.objID JOIN SpecObjAll as s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid JOIN galSpecExtra as g ON g.specobjid = s.specobjid ORDER BY x.up_id &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
